289
00:14:38,320 --> 00:14:39,560
His heart meridian was damaged.

290
00:14:39,570 --> 00:14:41,620
However, he drank your blood.
He's recovering rapidly.

291
00:14:41,640 --> 00:14:43,400
He's probably grinning
to himself somewhere.

292
00:14:43,840 --> 00:14:44,640
Grinning to himself?

293
00:14:44,880 --> 00:14:46,240
When Love Severance acts up,

294
00:14:46,460 --> 00:14:47,920
one will only kill the one they love.

295
00:14:48,320 --> 00:14:50,600
Now, he knows
that he's the one you love the most.

296
00:14:50,960 --> 00:14:53,680
He already forgot about the fact
that you would try to end his life.

297
00:15:00,920 --> 00:15:01,680
What's wrong?

298
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:04,000
When I think about
that arrogant look on his face,

299
00:15:04,360 --> 00:15:05,520
I feel like slapping him.

300
00:15:07,080 --> 00:15:07,760
Me too.

301
00:15:08,000 --> 00:15:09,920
Slap him on my behalf
when you have the chance.

302
00:15:10,520 --> 00:15:11,200
However,

303
00:15:11,280 --> 00:15:14,760
your sister and Zhang Mingkai
acted strangely

304
00:15:15,560 --> 00:15:17,640
after I told them about
the effect of Love Severance.

305
00:15:21,680 --> 00:15:22,480
I...

306
00:15:23,380 --> 00:15:25,110
Although Love Severance
is a potent voodoo,

307
00:15:25,120 --> 00:15:27,880
it shows who the victim
cares about the most.

308
00:15:28,480 --> 00:15:30,560
The person I care about the most
is definitely Yuhan.

309
00:15:31,640 --> 00:15:32,760
How could this be?

310
00:16:15,680 --> 00:16:16,560
I'm not asleep yet.

311
00:16:17,360 --> 00:16:19,720
I'm just passing by
on my way to the toilet.

312
00:16:20,360 --> 00:16:21,520
Did I wake you up?

313
00:16:22,320 --> 00:16:23,120
No.

314
00:16:24,140 --> 00:16:25,280
I'm waiting for your apology.

315
00:16:25,680 --> 00:16:26,480
Oh.

316
00:16:27,480 --> 00:16:28,480
You mean your injury?

317
00:16:30,160 --> 00:16:30,960
It hurts.

318
00:16:31,960 --> 00:16:33,040
But I'll survive.

319
00:16:35,600 --> 00:16:36,400
What about you?

320
00:16:37,480 --> 00:16:38,400
I'm fine.

321
00:16:38,720 --> 00:16:40,680
If there's nothing else,
I'll head back now.

322
00:16:40,780 --> 00:16:42,660
You're brushing me off
with your apology, huh?

323
00:16:42,820 --> 00:16:44,400
I almost died because of you, you know?

324
00:16:50,080 --> 00:16:51,520
You didn't die, did you?

325
00:16:52,160 --> 00:16:54,280
And, it's not like
I could control myself.

326
00:16:54,840 --> 00:16:56,200
I was struck by voodoo.

327
00:16:57,080 --> 00:16:57,880
You know

328
00:16:58,360 --> 00:17:00,080
