say something that disgusting.

350
00:18:06,640 --> 00:18:07,520
Go and throw up, then.

351
00:18:08,160 --> 00:18:09,280
I wish to tell you this.

352
00:18:10,320 --> 00:18:11,880
I'm not telling you to forget about him.

353
00:18:12,380 --> 00:18:14,320
After all,
he sacrificed his life to save you.

354
00:18:16,040 --> 00:18:17,240
I'm glad that you know that.

355
00:18:17,480 --> 00:18:18,280
However,

356
00:18:19,320 --> 00:18:21,360
